2011-05-10T08:44:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/powercom-co-ltd-april-sales-fall-9-41-table-3043-tt.html
POWERCOM CO LTD (3043)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 9.41% to NT$399,550,000 from NT$441,054,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales            399,550          441,054    
YOY%              -9.41%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,817,948        1,276,203   
YOY%              42.45% 
=================================================================
 